Cache custom built-in extensions to reduce excessive fetch requests

Adds an in-memory cache for the result of readCustomBuiltinExtensions()
in the web extensions scanner service, preventing redundant network
requests on every call to scanUserExtensions.

Index: code-editor-src/src/vs/workbench/services/extensionManagement/browser/webExtensionsScannerService.ts
===================================================================
--- code-editor-src.orig/src/vs/workbench/services/extensionManagement/browser/webExtensionsScannerService.ts
